8. O-O {White is ready to push e2-e4.} b6 {[%cal Gc8a6]} {Black can finish development now by either bringing the bishop to b7 or a6. Conceding the center without being forced to do so is in general a bad idea: 8...dxc4?! is premature and gives us what we want. 9.Qxc4⩲ .}
