12. e6 {Since the e5-pawn is lost we better give it up in this way, splitting Black's pawn structure and slightly weakening the black king. On top of that, the c8-bishop is a problematic piece that makes it difficult for Black to complete development.} fxe6 {[%csl Re6,Rc8]}
