11. Nge4 $5 {This move is far less popular and of a less forcing character than 11.Nxe6 , but is definitely worth having a closer look at. 11.Nxe6 fxe6 12.Qh5+ Ke7 13.Ne4 is our <a class="commentMoveSmall" href="/variation/18593191/#/13/w" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-tippy-content="Link to variation">mainline</a>. 11.Qh5 g6 12.Qh3 Be7 13.Nge4 ( 13.Nce4 Kf8 14.f4 Kg7 ) "r2qk2r/pb1nbp2/2p1p1pp/1p1nP3/2pPN3/2N3PQ/PP3PBP/R1B2RK1 b kq - 3 13" 13...Kf8} Qb6
