20. Rac1 {Better is 20.Rfc1! Qxd4 21.Qe2 Qb6 22.Bc7+- .} g5 {[%csl Re8]} {This is pushing the bishop away from a good diagonal, but now it is also clear that Black's king will never find safety as long as there are queens on the board.}
